ity and equityrelated products these products include equity swaps options warrants and futures overlying individual securities indices and baskets of securities and other equityrelated products morgan stanleys institutional equity division is a global leader in the origination distribution and trading of equity equitylinked and equityderivative securities their fixed income team deals in a diverse range of products including interest rate and currency products credit products derivatives and commodities marketer forward management llc forward management invests in strong wellmanaged companies that are trading below their intrinsic value longterm approach attempts to exploit market inefficiency created by investor emotion or nearterm misperceptions we believe that consistent application of our bottomup fundamental multifaceted valuation process will provide our clients competitive results with lower volatility in all market environments the firms investment strategies span virtually all asset glasses both domestic and abroadforward management employs bottomup fundamental research to identify potential investments they analyze a company to determine its true worth or intrinsic value and compare that value to the current market valuation to determine if there is an appropriate margin of safety for investment each potential investment must possess solid valuation strong fundamentals and catalysts which help to validate the underlying investment thesis they look for companies with low relative pb low relative pe low relative pricetocash flow low relative ps low relative evebitda that are trading below replacement value forward management also seeks companies with strong or improving cash flow high returns on capital low relative debt levels and a durable competitive advantage key catalysts include management changes a new product cycle andor restructuring that improves profitability nonprofit donations  grants     resurge international provide reconstructive surgery in 